</b><b></b><br><br>Because lead is a naturally occurring element in the Earth’s crust (found in soil, water, and air everywhere on the planet), it is very difficult for any sweet potato product to have "zero" lead. The goal is to source from soil that has the lowest possible background levels.&nbsp;By testing at 3-4 ppb (raw equivalent), our farmers have demonstrated that their soil is among the cleanest available.</span></p></div></section></div></div></div><script>
